{"TopicId":198063,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"automatically targeting","CreatedByName":"Claas2008","CreatedById":208121,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-12T13:27:09Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Claas2008","CreatedById":208121,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-12T13:27:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp dir=\u0022ltr\u0022\u003E\nI have a plane with a big missile in it, but I can\u0027t send it somewhere and that is very annoying. is there anything that allows me to aim it at a target (not an object or building) without controlling the missile?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-11-12T13:40:53Z\u0022 title=\u002211/12/2020 01:40  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 12, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Val\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EFixed fonts and formatting issue\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Claas2008","CreatedById":208121,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-12T13:51:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223880460\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198063\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221605187629\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022208121\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Claas2008\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 minutes ago, Claas2008 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp dir=\u0022ltr\u0022\u003E\nI have a plane with a big missile in it, but I can\u0027t send it somewhere and that is very annoying. is there anything that allows me to aim it at a target (not an object or building) without controlling the missile?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt needs to go to a target al by himself\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-12T13:53:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/208121-claas2008/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022208121\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/208121-claas2008/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Claas2008\u003C/a\u003E, are you using a weapons mod, or are you playing the stock game?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Claas2008","CreatedById":208121,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-12T13:53:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223880473\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198063\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221605189182\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/208121-claas2008/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022208121\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/208121-claas2008/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Claas2008\u003C/a\u003E, are you using a weapons mod, or are you playing the stock game?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWithout mods\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-12T13:56:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223880476\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198063\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221605189223\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022208121\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Claas2008\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Claas2008 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWithout mods\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen in that case, you just have to point the missile in the right direction and fire, and hope it flies straight.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 There\u0027s no way to have a missile lock onto a target without your input in the stock game.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Claas2008","CreatedById":208121,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-12T13:59:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223880480\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198063\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221605189361\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 minutes ago, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen in that case, you just have to point the missile in the right direction and fire, and hope it flies straight.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 There\u0027s no way to have a missile lock onto a target without your input in the stock game.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI tried a kerbnet waypoint, but you can\u0027t set it as a target\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223880480\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198063\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221605189361\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 minutes ago, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen in that case, you just have to point the missile in the right direction and fire, and hope it flies straight.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 There\u0027s no way to have a missile lock onto a target without your input in the stock game.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hope that in a update that is going to\u00A0change.\u00A0i also tried kerbnet waypoint, but you can only set your navigation on it and not a target\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-12T14:10:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223880483\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198063\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221605189582\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022208121\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Claas2008\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 minutes ago, Claas2008 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hope that in a update that is going to\u00A0change.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI highly doubt it will.\u00A0\u00A0 It\u0027s the Kerbal Space Program, not the Kerbal Aerial Combat Program.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 At least for the stock game.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou should take a look at the BDArmory mod.\u00A0\u00A0 It has weapons and targeting items in it.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Claas2008","CreatedById":208121,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-12T15:19:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223880491\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198063\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221605190238\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI highly doubt it will.\u00A0\u00A0 It\u0027s the Kerbal Space Program, not the Kerbal Aerial Combat Program.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 At least for the stock game.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou should take a look at the BDArmory mod.\u00A0\u00A0 It has weapons and targeting items in it.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nkerbnet helps you find a good landing spot.\u00A0if they change it so that you can make a waypoint your target you automatically go to you waypoint, then it helps not only landing, but targetting too\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jimmymcgoochie","CreatedById":199902,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-12T15:46:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUse a probe core with target mode \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E (enable all \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E modes on all probes in the save settings), put a target object out (flag, random part etc.), control the plane from the missiles probe core, set \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E to point to target, fire missile, quickly switch back to the plane and hope the missile sticks to the target tracking \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E mode.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut if you\u2019re going down the path of building air-launched missiles then BDArmory and its various expansion mods are the way to go.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-13T02:00:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223880519\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198063\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221605195993\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022199902\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022jimmymcgoochie\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, jimmymcgoochie said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nput a target object out (flag, random part etc.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYup, I misread the \u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E and thought he wanted to target a building, not an object.\u00A0 Got that backwards.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 It can work, but stock KSP is really not designed for this.\u00A0\u00A0 Get one of the mods.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-13T02:24:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223880506\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022198063\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221605194373\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022208121\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Claas2008\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, Claas2008 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nkerbnet helps you find a good landing spot.\u00A0if they change it so that you can make a waypoint your target you automatically go to you waypoint\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNothing in the stock game automatically goes to anything, waypoints, targets, or anything. And it likely never will.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs has been said, what you want to do is outside the scope of the game UI, even if it\u0027s inside the scope of what\u0027s possible to do in the game engine. Mods are the way to go to add the functionality to the UI/UX.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}